  <div class="col-lg-9 ml-sm-auto col-xl-10 pl-lg-0 pr-lg-5 px-xl-3">

    <div class="row ">
      <div class="col-lg-4 " id="chat--list">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-between align-items-center">
          <div class=" d-flex justify-content-between w-100">
            <h6 class="chat-list__title">Messages</h6>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
              <img class="mr-2" src="img/chat-icon-sm.svg" />
              <h6 class="chat-list__new-msg">New Messages</h6>
            </div>
          </div>

          <form class="w-100">
            <img class="chat-search--icon" src="img/search-icon-sm.svg" />
            <input class="py-4 pl-5 form-control chat-search-input" type="text"
              placeholder="Search or start a new message" aria-label="Search" />
          </form>
          <div class="breakline my-3"></div>

          <div class="w-100">
            <div class="align-items-center py-2 bg-white d-flex my-3 px-3 chat-item" id="chat-item">
              <img class="img-fluid " src="img/chat-img-1.png" alt="">
              <div class="sub-text d-flex flex-column ml-3 w-100">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-2">
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--name">Tomisin Lalude</h6>
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--time">4:50PM</h6>
                </div>
                <p class="text-selected mb-0 mr-3 chat-item--msg"><span class="msg-check"></span>Will you be at the
                  conference?</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="align-items-center py-2 bg-white d-flex my-3 px-3 chat-item" id="chat-item-2">
              <img class="img-fluid " src="img/chat-img-2.png" alt="">
              <div class="sub-text d-flex flex-column ml-3 w-100">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-2">
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--name">Nifemi Ajayi</h6>
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--time">4:50PM</h6>
                </div>
                <p class="text-selected mb-0 mr-3 chat-item--msg"><span class="msg-check"></span>I hope you are ready
                  for the internship?</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="align-items-center py-2 bg-white d-flex my-3 px-3 chat-item" id="chat-item-3">
              <img class="img-fluid " src="img/chat-img-3.png" alt="">
              <div class="sub-text d-flex flex-column ml-3 w-100">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-2">
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--name">Julia Orji</h6>
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--time">Yesterday</h6>
                </div>
                <p class="text-selected mb-0 mr-3 chat-item--msg"><span class="msg-check"></span>Designing a mind
                  blowing product is what i expect from you.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="align-items-center py-2 bg-white d-flex my-3 px-3 chat-item" id="chat-item-4">
              <img class="img-fluid " src="img/chat-img-4.png" alt="">
              <div class="sub-text d-flex flex-column ml-3 w-100">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-2">
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--name">Ayo Shittu</h6>
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--time">Yesterday</h6>
                </div>
                <p class="text-selected mb-0 mr-3 chat-item--msg"><span class="msg-check"></span>I just went through
                  your portfolio.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="align-items-center py-2 bg-white d-flex my-3 px-3 chat-item" id="chat-item-5">
              <img class="img-fluid " src="img/chat-img-5.png" alt="">
              <div class="sub-text d-flex flex-column ml-3 w-100">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-2">
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--name">Abiodun Popoola</h6>
                  <h6 class="my-0 chat-item--time">2d ago</h6>
                </div>
                <p class="text-selected mb-0 mr-3 chat-item--msg"><span class="msg-check"></span>Lorem ipsum dolor is
                  not good enough for mockup text.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col msg--wrap" id="msg--wrap">
        <p class="chat--list-back" id="chat--list-back">Back</p>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
          <div class="w-100 d-flex align-items-center">
            <div>
              <img class="img-fluid msg-pic" src="img/chat-img-1.png" alt="Adeleke">
            </div>
            <span class="ml-4 msg-name">Tomisin Lalude</span>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex">
            <img class="mr-1" src="img/mdi_attach_file.svg" />
            <img class="ml-1" src="img/mdi_more_vert.svg" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="msg--body bg-white mt-2">
          <div class="m-3">
            <div class="msgs-wrap">
              <div class=" msg-item">
                <p class="msg-item--text chat-bubble-1">If you intend to seek financial support from an investor,
                  a traditional business plan is a must.</p>
                <p class="msg-item--time">11:46 AM</p>
              </div>
              <div style="clear: both;"></div>
              <div class="msg-item--right">
                <p class="msg-item--text-right chat-bubble-2">Very correct.</p>
                <p class="msg-item--time-right">11:46 AM</p>
              </div>
              <div style="clear: both;"></div>
              <div class=" msg-item">
                <p class="msg-item--text chat-bubble-3">Thank you.</p>
                <p class="msg-item--time">11:52 AM</p>
              </div>
              <div style="clear: both;"></div>
              <div class="msg-item--right">
                <p class="msg-item--text-right chat-bubble-4">Will you be at the conference?</p>
                <p class="msg-item--time-right">11:57 AM</p>
              </div>
              <div style="clear: both;"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="msg--input d-flex">
              <img class="" src="img/mdi_insert_emoticon.svg" />
              <input class="msg--input-text" type="text" placeholder="Type something..." />
              <img class="msg--input-send" src="img/Send Icon.svg" />
            </div>
            <div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
